ovides a platform for developers to build, test, and deploy their applications.\\n3. DevOps: Elestio offers a range of tools and features that support DevOps practices, including continuous integration and continuous deployment (CI/CD).\\n4. Big data and analytics: Elestio can be used to deploy and manage big data and analytics workloads, including data lakes, data warehouses, and machine learning models.\\n\\nOverall, Elestio is a cloud-based platform that provides a flexible and scalable environment for deploying and managing applications, websites, and services.\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"stop\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":378,\"promptTokens\":42,\"totalTokens\":420}}}"}}
